<p>Spring is almost here for the northern hemisphere, and that means it&#039;s almost lightning season. It&#039;s time to talk UPSs and battery backups. Listen as John and Dave talk through all the permutations you&#039;ll need to know to choose the right UPS for your setup. On top of that, a few things in Cool Stuff Found, solving mailbox syncing problems, and a deep discussion about how to rip movies and then to get them onto your iPhone or iPad!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
